### ============================================================================
### 产品 API (Product API)
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/products
### ============================================================================

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 创建产品 (Create Product)
### Required fields: name, price, stock, category, sku
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 创建产品 - 无线耳机
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "无线降噪耳机",
  "description": "高品质主动降噪蓝牙耳机，支持30小时续航",
  "price": 299.99,
  "stock": 100,
  "category": "电子产品",
  "brand": "Sony",
  "tags": ["音频", "无线", "蓝牙", "降噪"],
  "sku": "WH-1000XM5",
  "active": true,
  "manufacturer": "索尼电子",
  "countryOfOrigin": "中国"
}

### 创建产品 - 跑步鞋
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "专业跑步鞋",
  "description": "轻量化设计，透气网面，适合长距离跑步",
  "price": 159.50,
  "stock": 50,
  "category": "运动户外",
  "brand": "Nike",
  "tags": ["鞋类", "跑步", "健身", "透气"],
  "sku": "NK-RUN-2024",
  "active": true,
  "manufacturer": "耐克体育",
  "countryOfOrigin": "越南"
}

### 创建产品 - 智能手表
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "智能运动手表",
  "description": "支持心率监测、GPS定位、50米防水",
  "price": 499.00,
  "stock": 30,
  "category": "电子产品",
  "brand": "Apple",
  "tags": ["智能穿戴", "运动", "健康", "GPS"],
  "sku": "AW-S9-2024",
  "active": true,
  "manufacturer": "苹果公司",
  "countryOfOrigin": "中国"
}

### 创建产品 - 咖啡机
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "全自动意式咖啡机",
  "description": "一键制作浓缩咖啡、卡布奇诺，内置研磨器",
  "price": 1299.00,
  "stock": 15,
  "category": "家用电器",
  "brand": "DeLonghi",
  "tags": ["厨房电器", "咖啡", "自动化"],
  "sku": "DL-ECAM22",
  "active": true,
  "manufacturer": "De'Longhi",
  "countryOfOrigin": "意大利"
}

### 创建产品 - 简化版（仅必填字段）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "基础商品",
  "price": 99.99,
  "stock": 10,
  "category": "其他",
  "sku": "BASIC-001"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 读取产品 (Read Product)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 获取所有产品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### 根据ID获取产品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 更新产品 (Update Product)
### All fields are optional for update
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 更新产品 - 完整更新
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "无线降噪耳机 Pro",
  "description": "升级版主动降噪蓝牙耳机，支持40小时续航，LDAC编码",
  "price": 399.99,
  "stock": 80,
  "category": "电子产品",
  "brand": "Sony",
  "tags": ["音频", "无线", "蓝牙", "降噪", "Hi-Res"],
  "sku": "WH-1000XM5-PRO",
  "active": true,
  "manufacturer": "索尼电子",
  "countryOfOrigin": "中国"
}

### 更新产品 - 仅更新价格和库存
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 349.99,
  "stock": 60
}

### 更新产品 - 下架
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 删除产品 (Delete Product)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
DELETE http://localhost:9200/products
### 删除产品
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/13

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 搜索产品 (Search Product)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 全文搜索 - 耳机
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=耳机&page=0&size=10

### 全文搜索 - 跑步
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=跑步&page=0&size=10

### 全文搜索 - 空关键字（返回所有）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=&page=0&size=20

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 高级搜索 (Advanced Search)
### Supports: keyword, category, brand, tag, manufacturer, active, minPrice, maxPrice, minStock, sortField, sortDirection
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 高级搜索 - 电子产品价格区间
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/advanced?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "电子产品",
  "minPrice": 100,
  "maxPrice": 1000
}

### 高级搜索 - 运动户外产品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/advanced?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "运动户外"
}

### 高级搜索 - 特定品牌
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/advanced?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Sony"
}

### 高级搜索 - 仅上架商品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/advanced?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": true
}

### 高级搜索 - 组合条件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/advanced?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "耳机",
  "category": "电子产品",
  "brand": "Sony",
  "minPrice": 200,
  "maxPrice": 500,
  "active": true
}

### 高级搜索 - 带排序
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/advanced?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "电子产品",
  "sortField": "price",
  "sortDirection": "asc"
}

### 高级搜索 - 库存筛选
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/advanced?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minStock": 20
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 聚合统计 (Aggregation)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 按类别聚合统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/aggregate/category

### 按类别聚合统计 - 过滤特定类别
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/aggregate/category?category=电子产品

### 按价格区间聚合统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/aggregate/price

### 按价格区间聚合统计 - 带类别过滤
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/aggregate/price?category=电子产品&minPrice=100&maxPrice=1000

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 搜索带聚合 (Search with Aggregations)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 搜索带聚合 - 无线
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search-with-aggregations?keyword=无线&page=0&size=10

### 搜索带聚合 - 电子产品带价格范围
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search-with-aggregations?keyword=耳机&category=电子产品&minPrice=200&maxPrice=500&page=0&size=10

### 搜索带聚合 - 完整参数
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search-with-aggregations?keyword=耳机&category=电子产品&minPrice=200&maxPrice=500&page=0&size=10

### ============================================================================
### Outbox 事件 API (Outbox Event API)
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/outbox
### ============================================================================

### 获取待发送的Outbox事件
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/pending

### 获取失败的Outbox事件
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/failed

### 重试失败的Outbox事件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/retry/1

### 删除Outbox事件
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/1

### 清理已完成的Outbox事件 (默认7天前)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/cleanup

### 清理已完成的Outbox事件 (指定天数)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/cleanup?daysOld=30
